<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>{{serviceName}} Subscription Notice</title>
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>{{serviceName}} Subscription Update</h1>
    <p>
      We hope this message finds you well. We're writing to inform you that the
      grace period for your
      {{serviceName}}
      subscription has ended, and as a result, your subscription has been
      respectfully terminated. Please be aware that all data linked to this
      subscription has been removed in accordance with our data retention
      policy.
    </p>
    <p>
      Additionally, we noted an outstanding invoice tied to this subscription.
      We want to clarify that this invoice has now been voided, rendering it
      invalid. We kindly ask that you refrain from sending any payments to the
      address specified in this voided invoice, as such transactions cannot be
      retrieved.
    </p>
    <p>
      If you would like to continue benefiting from our services, we invite you
      to create a new subscription at your convenience. Our team is on standby
      to assist you through this process.
    </p>
    <p>
      If you have any further queries or require additional assistance, please
      feel free to reach out to us. We value your partnership and are committed
      to serving your needs.
    </p>
    <p>With warm regards,</p>
    <p>The {{serviceName}} Team</p>
  </body>
</html>